# Pro User Management System

A modular, OOP-based User Management System with full CRUD, localStorage persistence, and responsive UI.

## Features

- Create, Read, Update, Delete Users
- Validation for name, email, and age
- Toast notifications for feedback
- Data persisted in localStorage
- Modular ES6 architecture

## How to Run

1. Clone this repo
2. Serve via a local server (VS Code Live Server or `npx serve`)
3. Open `index.html` in a browser
4. Add/Edit/Delete users and see real-time updates

